content: Assuming they are not corrupt, you can use each by - exiting TB - click windows key and 'r' key and then enter thunderbird.exe -p which invokes profile manager. click the create profile button, then next, then enter a name (e.g., profiletest), and then click the browse button to locate and select one of the profiles to view. Repeat that for each profile.
creator: davidsk
